data.description: Discover comfort and style in this inviting 3-bed, 2-bath home at 6 Ashly Ct, Hanover, PA. Open up the home to a nice sitting area sectioned off with cafe doors. Through there, the floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a bright and welcoming space. The kitchen is perfect for both daily living and entertaining guests. The private master suite, two additional bedrooms, and a second bathroom provide versatility for a growing family or those working from home. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, the property boasts a well-maintained yard and a one-car garage, offering both tranquility and convenience. Experience the charm of 6 Ashly Ct – schedule a showing today and make this your dream home!
